window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>After escaping Doragon’s clutches, Roy finds himself stranded in the Windblight, a harsh desert under the control of a rival clan - one that won’t think twice about tossing him in their fighting arena to pay off a perceived debt.</p> <p>Meanwhile, Aika, Ferry, and Hermit face their own problems in the form of retribution from the Itachi clan. While Hermit might be a Sovereign, his sister carries the same title.</p> <p>With enemies closing in on all sides, the three of them must work hard to stay ahead and continue on the trail of their abducted friend.</p>"; 
